723518f-a.title: Manhattan: Thompson Street - 3rd Street (West)
723518f-a.text:
Thompson Street, east side, north from West 3rd (formerly Amity) Street,
with Washington Square and the One Fifth Avenue apartment hotel in
the background. An outdoor art exhibition is going on; the druw-
ings and paintings are hung along the fence of the vacant 1ot where
240 to 248 Thorpson Street stood till about 1928.
November 17, 1932.
P. L. Sgerr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
